%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190727%2F59867499&h=efc79d15\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190727/59867499</a><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1367235/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1367235/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地嚴正警告！原居民切勿再與普羅大眾為敵，如果再有原居民傷害任何市民，我地一定會以一切專業知識，竭盡所能去肅清該村/鄉！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>最後，我地堅持要求政府回應5大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n撤回逃犯條例<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n撤控及釋放示威者<br />\n收回暴動定義<br />\n重啓雙普選</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>IF WE BURN, YOU BURN WITH US !!</strong></span>"},{"pid":"60b497b84ec0a5ac7c30aa3f5cf46cb67fd66226","tid":1369383,"uid":266635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:34:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4af5bbb31670db07c56e34094bfe0811263a2d1b","tid":1369383,"uid":276208,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:34:45.000Z","msg":"借位一用<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請幫推到鄉民見到，希望聽日可以相安無事</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">誠懇請鄉民今次真係要阻止任何可疑人士（包括疑似示威者）入村，唔係又引起誤會／衝突就唔好啦~~ </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[投訴懶人包] 反對套丁及冒充原居民 「修補撕裂，由我做起，幫助原居民保家衛族」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369127</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">齊上齊落，支持五大訴求<br />\n支持圍村去黑，還我平靜鄉郊<br />\n反恐反黑，由投訴撚做起</span></em>"},{"pid":"fdbfa827269aa08b2ca70c954667be763538e7bd","tid":1369383,"uid":241761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:34:47.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"d868afdd6e89f052d68b66efc9d7d73227353656","tid":1369383,"uid":263423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:34:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26e1eda3aad49d2bb111a274ab83eedda0628405","tid":1369383,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB